title: ► OFFICIAL SOUNDTRACK American Horror Story 5: HOTEL - "Heartbreak Hotel"
author: American Horror Story 10
description:
Music by: Heidi Feek - "Heartbreak Hotel".
American Horror Story: Hotel premieres Oct. 7th on FX and features Lady Gaga, Finn Wittrock, Matt Bomer, Sarah Paulson, Evan Peters, Lily Rabe, Angela Bassett, Kathy Bates, Naomi Campbell, Denis O’Hare, Cheyenne Jackson, Chloe Sevigny, Wes Bentley, Mara Winningham and Jessica Lange.
